  "Description": {
    "English": "A powerful upgrade to the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Neutron Cannon</span>. Additional resonance compressors allow significantly more energy to be routed through the cannon's central core, dramatically increasing operating power.<br><br>Installation will allow a fully-charged Neutron Cannon to launch <span class=\"name name-stellar\">additional projectiles</span> at <span class=\"name name-stellar\">higher speeds</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "强劲的<span class=\"name name-technology\">中子大炮</span>升级组件。此升级提供的额外共鸣压缩机将显著提高中子大炮核心接收的能量，并借此大幅提升功率。<br><br>安装此升级组件后，完全充能的中子大炮能够<span class=\"name name-stellar\">高速发射</span>一枚<span class=\"name name-stellar\">额外投射物</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">中子砲</span>的強力升級。額外的共振壓縮機能夠使大幅能量通過大砲的中央核心，顯著增加操作功率。<br><br>安裝後，能夠讓充滿能量的中子砲用<span class=\"name name-stellar\">更快的速度</span>發射<span class=\"name name-stellar\">額外射彈</span>。"
  },
